Version 4
SymbolType CELL
RECTANGLE Normal -80 64 80 -64
TEXT 0 -75 Center 2 Load Cell
SYMATTR Prefix X
PIN 80 -48 RIGHT 8
PINATTR PinName Red (E+)
PINATTR SpiceOrder 1
PIN 80 -16 RIGHT 8
PINATTR PinName Black (E-)
PINATTR SpiceOrder 2
PIN 80 16 RIGHT 8
PINATTR PinName Green (A-)
PINATTR SpiceOrder 3
PIN 80 48 RIGHT 8
PINATTR PinName White (A+)
PINATTR SpiceOrder 4
